The `sonicforever` binary shipped in this port is a custom build of the
RSDKv4 decompilation by spec58, configured for compatibility with the
Sonic Forever mod.

Project pages:
  https://teamforeveronline.wixsite.com/home
  https://teamforeveronline.wixsite.com/home/sonic-1-forever

The binary is only invoked when a mobile-format `Data.rsdk` is present AND
the user has enabled the Sonic Forever mod (set `SonicForeverMod=true` in
`mods/modconfig.ini`). With Origins data, the standard `RSDKv4` binary is
used instead.

Team Forever's RSDKv4 fork (the source of spec58's builds) is released
under the same RSDKv3/v4 Decompilation Source Code License v2 that governs
the upstream decomp — see `LICENSE.rsdkv4` in this folder for the full
text.

Upstream references:
  https://github.com/ElspethThePict/TeamForever-v4-1.3   (fork source)
  https://github.com/RSDKModding/RSDKv4-Decompilation   (parent decomp)

Thanks to spec58 for providing the custom binary. No modifications have
been made to it for this port; it ships as provided by the Sonic Forever
team.
